<br>
The trick is to get in as a tag along for a group doing the cleric epic, that would certainly mow through the FG's with the sort of power it takes to take down Zordak and the dragon that spawns when he is killed (Zordacalicus or something like that).  Buy the spell, and gate out before they start.<br>
<br>
That said, I have had the spell for a couple months at least, and have used it all of 0 times.<br>
